sql:
SELECT DISTINCT metric_name 
FROM financial_metrics 
WHERE frequency = 'annually' OR frequency = 'quarterly';

SELECT message 
FROM notifications 
WHERE is_read = 0;

external_knowledge:
Active users are those flagged with 'is_active = 1'; report length is determined by the content's length in characters.;
Contribution in terms of reports refers to the count of reports generated by these active users.;
Average size of report content is the average length of the report content text.;
Biggest report refers to the report with the maximum content length.;
